# DozePlus

A lightweight and safe Android Doze optimization module designed to improve battery efficiency and idle state behavior.

---

## 🌐 Language / Idioma

- 🇺🇸 English: https://github.com/rebangkkuser/DozePlus/blob/main/README.mkdn  
- 🇧🇷 Português (Brasil): https://github.com/rebangkkuser/DozePlus/blob/main/README_pt-br.mkdn  

---

## ⚙️ Features

- Optimizes Android Doze behavior
- Reduces background process load during idle state
- Lightweight service-based execution
- No persistent background processes
- Safe and reversible system changes

---

## 📱 Requirements

- Android 8.0+ (API 26 or higher)
- Magisk installed
- Root access enabled

---

## 📦 Installation

1. Download the latest release
2. Open Magisk Manager
3. Install the module from storage
4. Reboot your device

---

## 🔧 How it works

DozePlus applies system tuning at boot using Magisk service scripts:

- Enables battery optimizations during idle state
- Adjusts background process limits
- Restores normal behavior when device is active

---

## 📊 Behavior

| State | Action |
|------|--------|
| Idle | Battery optimized mode |
| Active | Normal system behavior |

---

## ⚠️ Notes

- This module does not modify system partitions
- All changes are systemless
- Focused on stability over aggressive tweaks

---

## 🧪 Status

Work in progress (v1.0 base)

